comments: LaVine (CHI) and Black (ORL) come together, causing marginal contact to occur off-ball.
Black (ORL) establishes himself in Williams' (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Caruso (CHI) reaches in and initiates contact to Wagner's (ORL) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Wagner's (ORL) shot attempt does not make contact with the rim, and the 24-second shot clock expires.
Isaac (ORL) moves alongside Vucevic's (CHI) path and maintains a legal guarding position as he contests Vucevic's driving shot attempt.
Both Banchero (ORL) and Caruso (CHI) engage and separate in marginal arm contact off-ball.

Replay review of the foul called on Suggs (ORL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Replay confirmed Suggs (ORL) initiates contact as he grabs Caurso's (CHI) jersey prior to him blocking the shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Wagner (ORL) makes an errant pass and the ball goes out of bounds.
Williams (CHI) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Wagner's (ORL) path during the screen.
Vucevic (CHI) is jumping toward the rebound when he makes clean contact with the ball as marginal contact occurs with Black (ORL).
Suggs (ORL) is established inbounds when he releases the ball.
LaVine (CHI) commits a take foul on Banchero (ORL).
Wagner (ORL) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
White (CHI) commits a take foul on Black (ORL).
Isaac (ORL) legally contests LaVine's (CHI) jump shot attempt.
Isaac (ORL) establishes himself in Caruso's (CHI) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Banchero (ORL) lifts and replants his left pivot foot after his gather in the lane.
Caruso (CHI) legally contests Banchero's (ORL) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
